 ***** DETERMINATION OF LATTICE CHARACTER AND BRAVAIS LATTICE *****

 A lattice character is consistent with the observed diffraction pattern
 for low values for the QUALITY OF FIT and if their implicated
 UNIT CELL CONSTANTS do not violate the ideal values by more than
